hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Do you know what extension he's on? crossbordermedication.com Things often go badly for Kimmie when she embarks on her search for fun -- but the point, says Wilson, is that Kimmie takes a shot even when it doesn't go well. "The purpose of the show to me is to really inspire girls who don't think they're cool and popular and pretty and all that to get out there and realize they can have a social life, too." There are sad story lines, of course, "but when we present the wins for my character, it's awesome"
